tech.mcprison.prison.modules

Class Module

  • java.lang.Object
    • tech.mcprison.prison.modules.Module
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PluginEntity

    public abstract class Module
extends java.lang.Object
implements PluginEntity
    Represents a module, which is a part of Prison that can be enabled and disabled independently from the rest of the modules.
    Since:
    API 1.0
